{"tid":2416631,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[慎選疫苗]  德國BioNTech疫苗會成為標記，更易中第二波生化襲擊","createTime":"2021-02-21T08:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T08:58:25.000Z","uid":30988,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7867cb9b9eaffb09112cddbeaf5d1411b1975163","tid":2416631,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"事實，武肺係某國軍方製造嘅生化武器。<br />\n軍情，一個病毒點先可以殺鬼佬，又保番自軍唔死？<br />\n事實二，70 億人基因變化極多，要客製化病毒較難入手<br />\n疫苗，rDNA 版本係貴嘢，某國人亦會用翻國貨，唔會打。<br />\n客製化病毒，可以針對某基因受體，正如武肺主要係改變丹山病毒去迎合人體ace2受體令人容易感染但其他動物相較不受影嚮。同樣，軍方將會針對rDNA 呢個基因段去研製新病毒。到時成套生化攻擊先算完成。<br />\n現時第一波某國靠賄賂局部科學界去頂住言論，各國亦要應付疫情，無力打擊邪惡國度。<br />\n第二波時，打rDNA 嘅將會死鳩哂，想報仇都唔會有機會。<br />\n立此存照。"},{"pid":"22872cb2a8c3bf8f74142132858aa2a6b53db996","tid":2416631,"uid":379586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:21:31.000Z","msg":"乜係rDNA？你想講mRNA？"},{"pid":"ad299d6db8ef36ce59536e5b5086abec8cfc0619","tid":2416631,"uid":29917,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22872cb2a8c3bf8f74142132858aa2a6b53db996","tid":2416631,"uid":379586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:21:31.000Z","msg":"乜係rDNA？你想講mRNA？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"問咁多仲乜，講你都唔會明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n介紹你睇多d有關地球唔係圓既資料"},{"pid":"3af91c846f0323b59122d309be9110a61e828e5e","tid":2416631,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"想講mrna？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nrdna唔係a卡版dlss咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c71ca4279a6c1f8116f4fb570260f2598c20693","tid":2416631,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:56:24.000Z","msg":"Yes, mRNA <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32df3a66a3c227bd6cf7932b346664fc131e533","tid":2416631,"uid":78